{"tid":1386900,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"[陰謀論]林鄭其實下緊一盤極大極邪惡既棋","createTime":"2019-07-30T12:15:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T03:59:46.000Z","uid":9683,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"70d39c478b23a2b8b27bc4a91049715de69322d3","tid":1386900,"uid":9683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T12:15:49.000Z","msg":"777依排剩係識不斷引火，一直都口提唔會成立獨立調查委員會。唔知佢有心定無意，硬係覺得佢係特登不斷連事件升溫務求令示威者行動加劇，另外從而不斷製造主角光環比黑警，令黑警做野更加出盡力，亦都令黑警成為套戲既大奸角boss。<br />\n<br />\n但其實大家有冇諗過，777 咁樣講係令到黑警對777既期望不斷咁升高。調轉頭諗，當示威者行動不斷咁升級，黑狗又不斷升級武力，令到更多市民討厭黑警，其實係一步一步咁隔離左黑警既退路。<br />\n<br />\n之前元朗事件就已經係其中一個斷絕黑警後路既好表現，經過依次事件，相信依家冇幾多黑社會會再肯幫黑警做野。<br />\n<br />\n萬一黑狗打贏示威者，777就順理成章贏左，但萬一黑狗攪唔掂示威者又點呢？<br />\n<br />\n正所謂趕狗入窮巷，當黑警再冇後路之時，如果依個時候777主動投誠命令成立獨立調查委員會煮9班黑警，到時就真係黑狗做軍政府取代777。<br />\n<br />\n變成就令解放軍明正言順咁出兵打黑狗，順而接管香港，唔使等2047就完成收回香港依個目標。<br />\n<br />\n黑狗，在情在理在邏輯上，但會比人放棄，即係死硬。"},{"pid":"af500e0b06437a9a45d08c1c73a5863986336ddc","tid":1386900,"uid":9683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T12:20:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c953862155ccc61e7281a164bf33e8247f8d83dc","tid":1386900,"uid":12890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T12:21:19.000Z","msg":"鄰國已經講明左唔會出軍隊"},{"pid":"f5fa66868dcac819bc3516a9f9af8acb37d167ec","tid":1386900,"uid":9683,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"c953862155ccc61e7281a164bf33e8247f8d83dc","tid":1386900,"uid":12890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T12:21:19.000Z","msg":"鄰國已經講明左唔會出軍隊"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T12:26:25.000Z","msg":"鄰國講野可信性係零"},{"pid":"1c51033e38511dbfb23e73aafb0fad314427cfa3","tid":1386900,"uid":9683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T12:45:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c55aa02dc0c9059b45423be3785c4ce96dafa034","tid":1386900,"uid":140041,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:24:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i2.kknews.cc/SIG=21eq9pk/ctp-vzntr/1523333619021n7678o76or.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.kknews.cc%2FSIG%3D21eq9pk%2Fctp-vzntr%2F1523333619021n7678o76or.jpg&h=32f69ede&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i1.sinaimg.cn/history/2014/1211/U11647P1488DT20141211110807.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi1.sinaimg.cn%2Fhistory%2F2014%2F1211%2FU11647P1488DT20141211110807.jpg&h=223832b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.kknews.cc/SIG=b6n8vv/31230001740qno4796o4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.kknews.cc%2FSIG%3Db6n8vv%2F31230001740qno4796o4.jpg&h=754e4416&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.anderson.ucla.edu/images/2017/sites/faculty/review%20publication/AR-french-rev-hero.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.anderson.ucla.edu%2Fimages%2F2017%2Fsites%2Ffaculty%2Freview%2520publication%2FAR-french-rev-hero.jpg&h=b43fbb36&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"228b41b536e4bf20e3f06fe145d3ad3a6e12b915","tid":1386900,"uid":180586,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:50:40.000Z","msg":"仲講777，777擺到明已經係一個路人。"},{"pid":"01269e6073bb444298be95b7775c8e94cd1397f3","tid":1386900,"uid":85694,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:54:53.000Z","msg":"相信777係諗過等解放軍落香港行一圈<br />\n等班人驚<br />\n中共所以7 29開記招公開唔比解放軍落黎<br />\n並叫佢食自己"},{"pid":"7f60bfe165f7a150e8cbf5654d66506db8fed948","tid":1386900,"uid":91017,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:03:50.000Z","msg":"警隊係林鄭唯一張牌, 佢唔支持警隊冇人會保佢!<br />\n但警隊細既已經頂唔順, 即係最後警隊會怨林鄭，所以成個政府其實特首只要講一句話成立獨委管同撤送中法, 遊行人就會少, 冇人出來行, 警隊就唔洗做到隻狗! <br />\n所以其實林鄭盤棋宜家咁係雙炒, 冇人會贏!"},{"pid":"a6a033cb131610bdccd60017be32a2e92b9e5e4c","tid":1386900,"uid":91017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:07:42.000Z","msg":"重有所謂壽終